author: Times Of India
title: Coronavirus: 6 who attended Nizamuddin congregation die of Covid-19
description: Six people from Telangana who attended a religious congregation in Delhi's Nizamuddin between March 13 and 15 died due to novel coronavirus, the state government said on Monday.
